help: Move module level imports to top of file
1  | #!/usr/bin/python3
2  | 
3  | """docstring"""
4  + import os
5  | 
6  | from __future__ import annotations
7  | 
8  | print("something")
9  | 
   - import os
10 | 
11 | # Prevent F403
12 | os.path
note: This is an unsafe fix and may change runtime behavior
